                            <comment id="12637351" author="hossman" created="Tue, 7 Oct 2008 03:33:21 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;I would think it might just make sense to include all of the lucene contrib jars in the release, but only put the &quot;major&quot; ones the war &amp;#8211; then people who want added the added functionality of some of the contribs can just include them by adding them to solr/lib (or @sharedLib)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;adding all contribs to the war seems like unnecessary bloat for the average user.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12670775" author="shalinmangar" created="Thu, 5 Feb 2009 15:10:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Marking for 1.5&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
